            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-05-13T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-05-14T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-05-12T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-05-13T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Sunny. Light winds becoming northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the late evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 9 and 12 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
